The paper discusses the application of VO2-based oscillators in oscillatory neural networks, indicating a focus on the intersection of neuroscience and engineering. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also discusses physical mechanisms and circuit design, suggesting a focus on Electrical Engineering and Electronic Circuits (cs.ET) and Electromagnetism (cs.EM). The paper also explores synchronization and coupling in oscillator circuits, indicating a focus on Systems and Control (cs.SY) and Computer Engineering (cs.CE).
